<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1456.Apologies_to_Thucydides"><img alt="Apologies to Thucydides: Understanding History as Culture and Vice Versa" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1328872674l/1456._SX98_.jpg" />
